{"type": "article", "id": 13056, "title": "ifilm X-T1 IR 无反相机", "description": "", "date": "2015-08-05T07:00:19Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 12, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606000202vMBpnV2FqQS1fudU.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\tFujifilm 最近推出 X-T1 变种型号 X-T1 IR，后者在外形和功能上与前者相似，但是它是 X 系列中首部具备红外线摄影功能的无反相机。相对于前者，它可以捕捉红外线以及部分紫外线画面，因此也会主要应用于科研、医疗等领域。相机将于今年 10 月正式推出，售价 1699 美元（约合10550 人民币）。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140721T6uJyM8zcq2VOUxo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201607261407218fODMcuIn2aAFRH3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140722eCA71kq8whWixKgL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66601562\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140722G0UTFdo1PQvsRSYC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n\n"}